PI:

1: 3V3
19: MOSI SPI0
23: CLK SPI0
31: DISPLAY RASPI ENABLE
33(29 on board): DISPLAY LIGHT DISABLE
37: DISPLAY RESET

2: 5V
6: GND
8: UART TX
12: CE SPI1
16: IMPULSE_INPUT
18: DC SPI0
22: BOXIÂ²BUS SYNC
24: CE SPI0
32: DC SPI1
38: MOSI SPI1
40: CLK SPI1

Arduino:
D0: UART RX
D1: UART TX
D6: DMX OUT
D7: PULSE IN
D8: DISPLAY LIGHT
D9: DISPLAY D/C
D10: DISPLAY CE
D11: DISPLAY MOSI
D13: DISPLAY CLK
A4: PWM SDA
A5: PWM CLK
A6: BRIGHTNESS IN
